Summary.
MANOWAR live - at their best Shot from over 150 camera angles, using 
helicopters and camera cranes this program includes the Viking Encore 
set from the 2007 Demons, Dragons and Warriors tour plus full-length 
versions of Sons Of Odin, Glory, Majesty, Unity, Gods Of War and many 
others plus highlights from Turkey, Spain, Czech Republic, 
USA and Canada.
